      <bioghist encodinganalog="545">
         <head>Biographical History</head>
         
      <p>Charles R. Snyder was an American attorney, apparently specializing in cases involving railroads and public utilities such 
	  as power companies.</p></bioghist>
      
      <scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
         <head>Scope and Contents of the Collection</head>
         <p>The <emph render="bold">Charles R. Snyder Collection</emph> contains correspondence, corporate records, letterbooks and 
		 other material relating to Snyder's law practice.</p>
      </scopecontent>
      
      <arrangement encodinganalog="351$a">
